-- Freeberg Discusses New Book `The Age of Edison' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-08-01T19:20:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-01/freeberg-discusses-new-book-the-age-of-edison-audio-.html
Ernest Freeberg, professor of 
humanities at the University of  Tennessee , discusses his new 
book, "The Age of Edison: Electric Light and the Invention of 
Modern America", and Thomas Edison's role in the creation of the
electric light bulb.  Freeberg talks with Bloomberg's Kathleen 
Hays and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:50
 